feat: referred-aware badges, Under Review count, and Search decision filter

- Stage badge is decision-aware: referred shows "Under Review" (not "Quote"),
  declined shows no stage badge; only bound shows "Policy". Threaded the
  decision through dashboard, search, admin, customers, and policy detail.
- Customers card splits the per-customer count into Quotes vs Under Review.
- Search gains a Decision filter (Accepted / Declined / Referred), wired
  through the search API and CSV export.
- Dashboard Recent Policies and Cancelled Policies rows now show the full
  badge summary (Accepted + Policy + Paid/Unpaid/Cancelled).

